    "SBM (score-based matching) models utilizex t = x t-1 + σ 2 t -σ 2 t-1 ϵ t 1 ≤ t ≤ T(21)for some noise scales {σ t } typically set as a geometric sequence, which again ensure in the limit that the fully noised distribution is equivalent to N (0, I).",
